                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="56r" to="61r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT3138Negeranni"/>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        አን፡ ገብርከ፨ ገብረ፡ ኄር፡ <add>ዮሴፍ፡</add> ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ አሜን፨ ወአሜን፨
                     </explicit>
